            "pop_detail": "Top Notes <p>  Citronella Java - A fresh and citrusy oil with natural insect repellent properties. </p><p>   Eucalyptus Peppermint - A fresh and uplifting scent insect-repelling scent with a woody-sweet undertone. </p><p>   Middle Notes </p><p>  Niaouli - A camphorous oil with a fresh, minty aroma and eucalyptus-like scent. </p><p>   Lavender - Fresh and grassy, this fragrant oil freshens and softens the blend.    Geranium - a floral and rosy oil that creates a calming and grounding effect.</p>",
            "showplus": true,
            "PoopupIconCode": "<div>\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Citronella.png?v=1688467258\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Niaouli.png?v=1688467255\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Eucalyp.png?v=1688467257\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/geranium02.png?v=1688467257\">\n        </div>\n<div>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0360/1347/3931/files/Lavender.png?v=1688467256\">\n        </div>\n<div></div>"
