            "detail": "A wonderfully floral and calming scent reminiscent of warm summer evenings. Tap to discover more>",
            "pop_heading": "Linden & Lavender",
            "pop_detail": "Top Notes <p> White Grapefruit - A sweet and fruity oil that’s known for its uplifting and energising properties. </p><p> Middle Notes </p><p> Linden Blossom - Extracted from the delicate, yellow flowers of the Linden tree - it’s a warm, floral and somewhat honey-like aroma with relaxing effects. </p><p> Neroli - Extracted from the flowers of bitter orange trees, this oil has a sweet, floral, citrus aroma. </p><p> Lavender - A delicate, floral scent with grassy, herbal notes. Famed for its calming, sedative properties.</p>",
